# .NET build output — local builds (e.g. on Windows) bake `obj/project.assets.json`
# with host-only NuGet paths. If these dirs leak into the container they
# override the in-container `dotnet restore` and `dotnet publish` fails with
# NETSDK1064: Package <X> was not found.
**/bin/
**/obj/

# Bot worker secrets — Compose mounts these via `env_file:` at runtime, the
# image never needs them. Keeps SL credentials out of layer history.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Editor / VCS noise
.vs/
.vscode/
.idea/
*.user
.DS_Store

# Docs and meta — not needed inside the image
README.md
.gitignore
